## Project: Livny Health EHR
Modern, clean EHR with ice/Nordic aesthetic. Current focus: physician prescribing workflow.

## Stack
React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind + FastAPI

## Standards
- Named exports, TypeScript strict mode
- Tailwind only (no CSS modules)
- Ice theme: glacier-blue, deep-ice, arctic
- 8px spacing: tight/normal/comfortable/generous
- Cards > tables, white space > clutter
- Progressive disclosure, 2-3 actions max

## Component Rules
- UI components → `src/components/ui/`
- Domain components → `src/components/{domain}/`
- Include loading/error/empty states
- Follow template in COMPONENT_PATTERNS.md
- Reuse existing before creating new

## Design Principles
- Generous white space
- Subtle shadows (not borders)
- Max 3 colors per screen
- 15px min font size
- One primary task visible

## Don't
- Default exports
- Inline styles
- Heavy borders
- Table layouts (prefer cards)
- Cramped content
